- The delivery status 'Late' implies a delay in shipment, which could impact customer satisfaction; 
- The average order value for each customer and product can help identify trends in purchasing behavior; 
- Analyzing shipment efficiency can inform logistics and supply chain optimization strategies.

Active customers are those with 'is_active' set to 1 in the customers table; 
Total amount spent refers to the sum of all order totals for a customer; 
Loyalty points are accumulated by customers for rewards; 
The results are ordered from the highest total spend to the lowest.
